These are release notes for Altoros Heartbeat for PCF.

##<a id="ver"></a> v0.8.90

**Release Date:** July 20, 2017

Features included in this release:

* Open Beta.
* Pivotal Cloud Foundry monitoring with predefined dashboards.
* UAA integration.
* The possibility to use the service in a multitenant mode.
* Services monitoring (RabbitMQ, Redis, MySQL, Crunchy PostgreSQL, Dingo PostgreSQL) with predefined dashboards.
* Basic apps monitoring with predefined dashboards.
* JMXTrans integration.

Known issues in this release:

* Creation of service instances inside the org/space that grant users admin access to Altoros Heartbeat (the org/space specified at the Grafana configuration step during the installation process) is not supported.  
* After renaming the org/space with the Altoros Heartbeat service instance, monitoring of this org/space is terminated. Please contact Altoros for instructions on how to fix issue manually.
* Alerts are not enabled automatically after installation of the Altoros Heartbeat for PCF tile. To enable alerts, open the **alerting** dashboard and click the save icon.
